<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Artroom is an interior design studio creating beautiful, 
                                    functional spaces for residential and commercial clients.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ubuntu:wght@700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@100;200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/navbar.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/footer.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/homepage.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/animations.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/staticImages/favicon-32x32.png">
  <title>Artroom - Homepage</title>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/">
      <div id="logo"><img src="/staticImages/logo.png" alt="artroom logo" class="artroom-logo"></div>
    </a>
    <div id="hamburger">
      <div class="line"></div>
      <div class="line"></div>
      <div class="line"></div>
    </div>
    <nav id="navbar">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/" class="navbar-link active">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/projects" class="navbar-link">Projects</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/about" class="navbar-link">About</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/prices" class="navbar-link">Pricing</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/contacts" class="navbar-link">Contacts</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <select name="language" id="language" class="language-select">
            <option value="sk">Slovenčina</option>
            <option value="en" selected>English</option>
          </select>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>


  <div id="welcome-banner">
    <h1>Welcome to Artroom!</h1>
    <p>The team of experienced designers and architects.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="gen-banner">
    <div id="g-banner-text" class="hidden">
      <h2>Interior, exterior design and 3D visualization in EU</h2>
      <p>ARTROOM is a team of professionals. We design flats, cottages, restaurants, bars, offices, shops, and other residential and public premises.</p>
      <p>We also develop individual projects for low-rise private residential buildings and perform architectural 3D visualisation.</p>
      <p>We have a huge number of successfully completed projects and many years of experience in this field. The specialists in our studio will prepare for you detailed technical documentation of the highest quality, so you can fully implement the object.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="advantages-header">Our Advantages</h1>
  <div id="advantages-grid">
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/access-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>A PERSONALISED APPROACH</h3>
      <p>Individual approach to each customer, rather than imposing their perceptions</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/building-plan.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>FULL SERVICE PACKAGE</h3>
      <p>Full service package from drawings to authoring</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/building-tool-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>3D VISUALISATION</h3>
      <p>High-quality and realistic 3D visualisation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/building.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>FROM THE ROOM TO THE WHOLE SITE</h3>
      <p>The possibility of ordering the interior design of the entire property or of an individual room</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/construction-worker-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>CONSTRUCTION TEAMS</h3>
      <p>Possibility of realising the project with our construction crews</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/science-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>TECHNOLOGY</h3>
      <p>Use of innovative engineering technology and the latest construction materials in the design project</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/quality-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>QUALITY</h3>
      <p>The quality of our work is confirmed by the recommendations of our customers</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item hidden">
      <img src="/staticImages/question-circle-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="icon" width="45px" height="45px">
      <h3>FREE CONSULTATIONS</h3>
      <p>Free advice from highly qualified professionals when buying a flat, plot or house, or when carrying out a design project.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="works-header">SOME OF OUR WORKS</h1>
  <div id="works-showbanner" class="hidden slow">
    <% const project1 = projects[0] %>
    <% const project2 = projects[1] %>
    <% const project3 = projects[2] %>
    <div class="works-project">
      <a href="/projects/<%= project1._id %>"><img src="/uploads/<%= project1.images[0] %>" alt="Artroom design project"></a>
      <div class="works-name">
        <h3><%= project1.name %></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="works-project">
      <a href="/projects/<%= project2._id %>"><img src="/uploads/<%= project2.images[0] %>" alt="Artroom design project"></a>
      <div class="works-name">
        <h3><%= project2.name %></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="works-project">
      <a href="/projects/<%= project3._id %>"><img src="/uploads/<%= project3.images[0] %>" alt="Artroom design project"></a>
      <div class="works-name">
        <h3><%= project3.name %></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="contacts-link">
	<h2>For further information</h2>
	<a href="/contacts">Contact us</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <h5>Contact Information:</h5>
        <p class="address">Mozartova 4912/10,<br> 811 02 Bratislava - Stare Mesto</p>
        <p class="email">Email: <a href="mailto:artroom.box@gmail.com">artroom.box@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p class="phone-number">Phone number: +421 949 227 794</p>
      </div>
      <div class="working-hours">
        <h5>Working Hours:</h5>
        <p>Monday-Friday - 10:00-18:00</p>
        <p>Saturday-Sunday - not working</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="copyright">
    <p> © ARTROOM Architectural Studio.
      All rights reserved.
      All visual materials on the website belong to the ARTROOM architectural studio.
      Copying of any materials by third parties without written permission is prohibited. </p>
  </div>
  
  <script src="/scripts/language.js"></script>
  <script src="/scripts/navbar-transparent.js"></script>
  <script src="/scripts/navbar.js"></script>
  <script src="/scripts/animations.js"></script>

</body>

</html>